T1  - A Dynamic Model for Binary Panel Data With Unobserved Heterogeneity Admitting a √n-Consistent Conditional Estimator
AU  - Bartolucci, Francesco
AU  - Nigro, Valentina
Y1  - 2010/03/01
PY  - 2010
DA  - 2010/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA7531
